âš ï¸  GOOGLE CALENDAR NOTE
================================================================================

If Google Cloud app is in "Testing" mode, refresh tokens expire after 7 days.

To fix (one-time):
1. Go to: https://console.cloud.google.com
2. APIs & Services â†’ OAuth consent screen
3. Click "PUBLISH APP"

This keeps the "unverified app" warning during admin setup but tokens won't expire.

